             was indicted for <rs id="t17930529-25-off132" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-25-off132" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-25-off132" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930529-25-cd133" type="crimeDate">30th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-25-off132 t17930529-25-cd133"></join>, eight pair of mens leather shoes, value 38 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930529-25-victim322" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Muir
